217
00:24:09,039 --> 00:24:10,160
[SPEAKER_00] Teško je pokazati se.

218
00:24:11,279 --> 00:24:13,599
[SPEAKER_01] Je, ali ja mislim da je teško isprva.

219
00:24:14,640 --> 00:24:15,599
